title: Phantoms of Reality
creator: Ray Cummings
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of Phantoms of Reality, by Ray Cummings. Read by Richard Kilmer. Red Sensua's knife came up dripping—and the two adventurers knew that chaos and bloody revolution had been unleashed in that shadowy kingdom of the fourth dimension. (Summary by Ray Cummings) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.
